          <p class='first-para'>
            I knew that, if the noble Baroness did not find acceptable my helpful amendments earlier, she would not find this one acceptable and I understand the reasons why. It just seems to me to be a gargantuan figure. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
            Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
