            It strikes me that in my lifetime, the value of land has been either fairly constant or it has increased. When it comes, however, to compensating business which is
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_29gc' title='Col. 29GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 October 2000 vol 617 c29GC' name='column_29gc' href='#column_29gc' rel='bookmark'>29GC</a>
