            On Question, amendment agreed to.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0617P0-04956'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0617P0_20001017_GCR_154' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Hayman</span> moved Amendments Nos. 21 to 23:
        <q>Page 3, line 20, leave out from ("scheme") to ("of") in line 22 and insert ("shall, in particular, specify&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) the description or descriptions of income losses and the description or descriptions of non-income losses in respect of which payments are to be made, and</li>
        <li>(b) the description or descriptions of businesses in respect of which payments are to be made,</li>
        </ol>
        but need not provide for the making of payments in respect of all income losses or all non-income losses or (as the case may be) in respect of all businesses.</q>
        <q>( ) A scheme shall also, in particular&#x2014;
        <q>( ) specify the basis or bases").</q>
