        <q>Page 3, line 45, at end insert &#x2014;</q>
        <q>("( ) In this section&#x2014;
        <ul>
        <li>"income losses" means losses of income, and</li>
        <li>"non-income losses" means losses other than income losses.").</li>
        </ul>
        </q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0617P0-04965'>
